# Keyboard setup (Poker 3)

- Swap command and alt keys to match mac setup inside Mac and Windows

# Audio interface setup

- Mic input
  - Full gain
  - +48v (on)

# Router setup

- [OpenDNS Family Shield](https://www.opendns.com/setupguide/?url=familyshield)

